OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,FThree more Scottish Labour MPs have
OL,7,Fjoined the opposition against Sir Keir
OL,8,FStarmer's leadership from within the
OL,9,Fparty, issuing calls for the Prime
OL,10,FMinister to quit.
OL,12,FThe MPs each released statements on
OL,13,FMonday evening saying they had lost
OL,14,Ffaith in Sir Keir's ability to lead,
OL,15,Fpointing to Scottish Labour's election
OL,16,Fresult last week.
OL,18,FA number of their colleagues had
OL,19,Fearlier called for the Prime Minister
OL,20,Fto go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
