OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778547792
OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,FMelanie Ward, the MP for Cowdenbeath
OL,7,Fand Kirkcaldy, was one of several
OL,8,FGovernment aides from across the UK
OL,9,Fwho quit to express their discontent.
OL,11,FGordon McKee, the Labour MP for
OL,12,FGlasgow South and a former
OL,13,Fparliamentary private secretary at the
OL,14,FDepartment for Work and Pensions, also
OL,15,Fsaid it was time for a change in
OL,16,Fleadership.
OL,18,FMaureen Burke, the Labour MP for
OL,19,FGlasgow North East, also joined the
OL,20,Fgrowing number of discontented MPs
OL,21,Fcalling for Sir Keir to step down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778547792
OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,FHowever, not all in the Scottish
OL,7,FLabour Party shared their views, with
OL,8,FPaisley and Renfrewshire North MP
OL,9,FAlison Taylor posting a message online
OL,10,Fsupporting Sir Keir.
OL,12,FMs Ward was the first Labour MP from
OL,13,Fnorth of the border to state her
OL,14,Fposition on Monday evening.
OL,16,FA number of other Scottish Labour MPs,
OL,17,Fsuch as Alloa and Grangemouth's Brian
OL,18,FLeishman, had previously called for
OL,19,FSir Keir to go.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
