SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778547792
OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,FIn a statement on social media, Ms
OL,7,FWard said: "Keir Starmer did important
OL,8,Fwork to change the Labour Party, and
OL,9,Fgoverning in a time like this will
OL,10,Fnever be easy.
OL,12,F"But the message from last week's
OL,13,Felections was clear; the Prime
OL,14,FMinister has lost the confidence of
OL,15,Fthe public to lead this change."
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@AOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
