OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,FPosting on X slightly later on Monday
OL,7,Fevening, Ms Burke said: "Despite two
OL,8,Fdecades of SNP failure, people were
OL,9,Freluctant to give Labour a hearing and
OL,10,Ftold me that they could not, in good
OL,11,Ffaith, vote Labour while Keir Starmer
OL,12,Fis Prime Minister.
OL,14,F"Our party owes Keir a debt of
OL,15,Fgratitude for his leadership, but we
OL,16,Fare bigger than one person.
OL,26,@oD@YOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
