PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778547792
OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,F"With a heavy heart, I am calling on
OL,7,Fthe Prime Minister to set out a
OL,8,Ftimetable for his departure and for
OL,9,Four party to have a period of
OL,10,Freflection with any and all candidates
OL,11,Fwilling to have the chance to put
OL,12,Fthemselves forward."
OL,14,FMr McKee said: "I'm deeply sad that
OL,15,Fwe're in this position and proud of
OL,16,Fwhat Keir Starmer achieved reforming
OL,17,Fthe Labour Party.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]vD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
