OL,3,CThree more Scottish Labour MPs join
OL,4,Ccalls for Starmer to quit
OL,6,F"However, the message in Glasgow and
OL,7,Facross the country in last week's
OL,8,Felections was clear; the Prime
OL,9,FMinister has lost the confidence of
OL,10,Fthe public."
OL,12,FHowever, Ms Taylor backed the Prime
OL,13,FMinister, who she said "was elected on
OL,14,Fa five-year mandate to change,
OL,15,Fprotect, defend, enrich our United
OL,16,FKingdom".
OL,18,FShe posted: "It's wrong not to back
OL,19,Fthe Leader. Just wrong. This is not
OL,20,Fthe way to go about such matters. Keir
OL,21,Fneeds supported by his team.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]uD@XOUxD@HO]zD@MOU
